ect": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "4167-4176附近我会多单止盈。然后开始减仓", "lou": 62, "content_length": 39, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1768355061}, {"pid": 854515180, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 29, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-01-14 10:01", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "到区间了 我清多单了<br/>现在哪个冲得多的就减一点。今天会减到55%-60%仓位  直到过本周股指交割日。", "lou": 63, "content_length": 87, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1768356119}, {"pid": 854516029, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 25, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-01-14 10:07", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "AI金融我因为没有找到合适的标 做的是指南针的T 我今天也会T出去。", "lou": 64, "content_length": 60, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1768356468}, {"pid": 854518270, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 35, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-01-14 10:22", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[quote][pid=854517663,45974302,126]Reply[/pid] [b]Post by [uid=14466954]狂奔的哈士奇[/uid] (2026-01-14 10:18):[/b]<br/><br/>结合狼大上周五回复，之前空仓忍不了两天进来当基石。<br/>那这两天，从心理上来说，昨天绿今天缩量红，就是引场外资金进来，然后当基石？[/quote]<br/>你看一下最近一周两融增加的量 特别是前天的。这些高位融资进来的钱他们出不去的。已经是基石了 这些热钱容易去追热点，所以那些热点会很麻烦。这些钱太活跃了", "lou": 65, "content_length": 151, "reply_to": 854517663, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1768357356}, {"pid": 854519970, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 56, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-01-14 10:32", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "轻指数 重个股 仓位内做横盘很久的那种突破 AI硬暂时不做<br/>我目前看好电池", "lou": 66, "content_length": 64, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1768357979}, {"pid": 854522323, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 17, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-01-14 10:46", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[quote][pid=854522055,45974302,131]Reply[/pid] [b]Post by [uid=39161094]堕落的信用证[/uid] (2026-01-14 10:45):[/b]<br/><br/>狼大我脑子现在卡住了。<br/>今天突破高点了你还是按计划收盘控制仓位到55左右还是正常的75？[/quote]<br/>55%-60%内", "lou": 67, "content_length": 14, "reply_to": 854522055, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1768358808}, {"pid": 854544476, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 85, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-01-14 13:15", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "如果下午有反抽 早上没减的 4161没突破过去  可能还有一次减仓机会<br/>急跌不割肉", "lou": 68, "content_length": 68, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1768367747}, {"pid": 854544859, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 308, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-01-14 13:19", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "早上我不想和你们交流那么低级的问题 我的操作值多少钱你们自己说", "lou": 69, "content_length": 60, "14": {"13": 4}, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1768367947}, {"pid": 854545257, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 65, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-01-14 13:22", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "注意了 如果再次跌破4141 继续放量 3个15分钟确认跌破  那刚才4161的减仓位下调。 早上没减的就要减", "lou": 70, "content_length": 87, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1768368136}, {"pid": 854546335, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 33, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-01-14 13:30", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[quote][pid=854545835,45974302,151]Reply[/pid] [b]Post by [uid=38320147]frjy[/uid] (2026-01-14 13:26):[/b]<br/><br/>润泽这个时候冲个板，是不是辨识度拉满了  <br/>不对 大位已经板了[/quote]<br/>AIDC是机构自己单开一桌，没有辨识度  柚子和散户量化都在航天 AI应用里面<br/>趁这个时候反起来吸引资金 如果弱就出场 强就合力 其实就是打辨识度 抢资源", "lou": 71, "content_length": 137, "reply_to": 854545835, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1768368634}, {"pid": 854548396, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 17, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-01-14 13:46", "subject": "", "alterinfo"